Name: UBERMOSH:SANTICIDE
About the game: UBERMOSH is a fast-paced arcade series that started in 2015 and was shaped by the amazing community's feedback each new volume. SANTICIDE, the sixth volume, adds new elements to the extensively tested gameplay. A must buy for arcade and top-down enthusiasts. Each match lasts 90 seconds and the quest is surviving in a gun-filled pit while defeating as many enemies as you can. Choose the Class Mods and Powers that fits best your playstyle, or do the opposite to polish your reflexes. Classic, Hardboiled and Santicide mode setups how fast the pit will fill. Rank and Achievements keep you on track beating your previous scores. Welcome back, to UBERMOSH.
